room_title: Escape room "The Outlaw of El Paso" by Portal Escape Rooms in Eugene
room_description: The most dangerous outlaw in the country rode into town last night. Coincidentally, the local saloon owner disappeared around the same time. Moreover, a nearby bank vault was recently robbed! I believe there’s a connection between these events. Sheriff Dubell is out of town, so it’s up to you to track down the two men and the missing gold. The law is in your hands now, partner, saddle up and deliver some wild west justice! Good luck, Deputy Jones.
